  "title": "The impact of parent's and spouses' education on divorce rates in Norway",
  "abstract": "According to both economic and sociological theory, a couple's divorce rate may be influenced by their own educational attainment, that of their parents, and whether they have taken further education after marriage, although predictions are ambiguous.",
